<pb n="0503b" ed="T" id="T02.0109.0503b"/>
<lb n="0503b01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 109 [No. 99(379), No. 110]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0503b02" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title><note n="0503013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0503013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0503013"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>轉法輪經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0503b03" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0503b04" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0503014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">後漢安息三藏＝後漢【宋】【元】，後漢安息國三藏法師【元】</note><note n="0503014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後漢安息三藏＝後漢【宋】，<todo type="i"/>後漢安息三藏＝後漢【元】，＝後漢安息國三藏法師【元】</note><app n="0503014"><lem wit="【大】">後漢安息三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">後漢</rdg></app>安世高譯</byline>
<lb n="0503b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0503b0501">聞如是：</p><p id="pT02p0503b0504" place="inline">一時，佛在波羅<note n="0503015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00178;＝柰【明】</note><app n="0503015"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00178;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">柰</rdg></app>國鹿野樹下坐，時
<lb n="0503b06" ed="T"/>有千比丘諸天神，皆大會<note n="0503016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">側＝畟【元】【明】</note><app n="0503016"><lem wit="【大】">側</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">畟</rdg></app>塞空中，於是有
<lb n="0503b07" ed="T"/>自然法輪，飛來當佛前轉。佛以手撫輪曰：
<lb n="0503b08" ed="T"/>「<note n="0503017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">止＝上【明】</note><app n="0503017"><lem wit="【大】">止</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上</rdg></app>！往者吾從無數劫來，為名色轉<note n="0503018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝更【三】</note><note n="0503018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受＝更【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503018"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">更</rdg></app>苦無
<lb n="0503b09" ed="T"/>量，今者癡愛之意已止，漏結之情已解，諸
<lb n="0503b10" ed="T"/>根已定生死已斷，不復轉於五道也。」輪即
<lb n="0503b11" ed="T"/><note n="0503019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">止＝上【元】</note><app n="0503019"><lem wit="【大】">止</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">上</rdg></app>。</p><p id="pT02p0503b1102" place="inline">於是，佛告諸比丘：「世間有二事墮邊行，
<lb n="0503b12" ed="T"/>行道弟子捨家者，終身不當與從事。何等二？
<lb n="0503b13" ed="T"/>一為念在貪欲無清淨志，二為<note n="0503020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猗＝倚【明】</note><app n="0503020"><lem wit="【大】">猗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">倚</rdg></app>著<note n="0503021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔身〕－【三】</note><note n="0503021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔身〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503021"><lem wit="【大】">身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>愛
<lb n="0503b14" ed="T"/>不能精進。是故退邊行，不得值佛道德<note n="0503022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">具＝真【三】</note><note n="0503022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">具＝真【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503022"><lem wit="【大】">具</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">真</rdg></app>
<lb n="0503b15" ed="T"/>人。若此比丘不念貪欲著身愛行，可得受中，
<lb n="0503b16" ed="T"/>如來最正覺得眼得慧，從兩邊度自致泥洹。
<lb n="0503b17" ed="T"/>何謂受中？謂受八直之道，一曰正見，二曰
<lb n="0503b18" ed="T"/>正思，三曰正言，四曰正行，五曰正命，六曰
<lb n="0503b19" ed="T"/>正治，七曰正<note n="0503023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">志＝念【三】</note><note n="0503023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">志＝念【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503023"><lem wit="【大】">志</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">念</rdg></app>，八曰正定。若諸比丘本<note n="0503024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">末＝未【元】【明】</note><app n="0503024"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">未</rdg></app>
<lb n="0503b20" ed="T"/>聞道，當已知甚苦為真諦，已一心受眼受禪
<lb n="0503b21" ed="T"/>思受慧見，覺所念令意解，當知甚苦<note n="0503025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">習＝集【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0503025"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡為
<lb n="0503b22" ed="T"/>真諦，已受眼觀禪思慧見，覺所念令意解，如
<lb n="0503b23" ed="T"/>是盡真諦。何謂為苦？謂生老苦、病苦，憂、悲、惱
<lb n="0503b24" ed="T"/>苦，怨憎會苦，所愛別苦，求不得苦，要從五陰
<lb n="0503b25" ed="T"/>受盛為苦。何謂苦<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>？謂從愛故而令復有樂
<lb n="0503b26" ed="T"/>性，不離在在貪&CB00540;，欲愛、色愛、不色之愛，是
<lb n="0503b27" ed="T"/><app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>為苦。何謂苦盡？謂覺從愛復有所樂，婬
<lb n="0503b28" ed="T"/>念不<note n="0503026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝愛【三】</note><note n="0503026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受＝愛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503026"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">愛</rdg></app>，不念無餘無婬，捨之無復禪，如是
<lb n="0503b29" ed="T"/>為<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡。何謂苦<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡欲受道？謂受行八直
<pb n="0503c" ed="T" id="T02.0109.0503c"/>
<lb n="0503c01" ed="T"/>道，正見、正思、正言、正行、正命、正治、正志、正定，
<lb n="0503c02" ed="T"/>是為苦<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡受道真諦也。</p>
<lb n="0503c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0503c0301">「又是，比丘！苦為真諦，苦由<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>為真諦，苦<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>
<lb n="0503c04" ed="T"/>盡為真諦，苦<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡欲受道為真諦，若本在昔
<lb n="0503c05" ed="T"/>未聞是法者，當受眼觀禪行受慧見受覺念
<lb n="0503c06" ed="T"/>令意得解。若令在斯未聞是四諦法者，當受
<lb n="0503c07" ed="T"/>道眼、受禪思、受慧覺，令意<note n="0503027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝得【三】</note><note n="0503027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行＝得【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503027"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">得</rdg></app>解。若諸在彼不
<lb n="0503c08" ed="T"/>得聞是四諦法者，亦當受眼、受禪、受慧、受覺，
<lb n="0503c09" ed="T"/>令意得解，是為四諦三轉合十二事，知而未
<lb n="0503c10" ed="T"/>淨者吾不與也。一切世間諸天人民，若梵、若
<lb n="0503c11" ed="T"/>魔、沙門、梵志，自知證已，受行戒、定、慧、解、<note n="0503028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">度＝受【明】</note><app n="0503028"><lem wit="【大】">度</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">受</rdg></app>知
<lb n="0503c12" ed="T"/>見成，是為四極。是生後不復有，長離世間無
<lb n="0503c13" ed="T"/>復憂患。」佛說是時，賢者阿若拘鄰等及八
<lb n="0503c14" ed="T"/><note n="0503029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">千＝十【三】</note><note n="0503029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">千＝十【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503029"><lem wit="【大】">千</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">十</rdg></app>&CB00108;天，皆遠塵離垢諸法眼生。其千比丘
<lb n="0503c15" ed="T"/>漏盡意解，皆得<note n="0503030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔阿〕－【三】</note><note n="0503030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔阿〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503030"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>羅漢，及上諸<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>法應當
<lb n="0503c16" ed="T"/>盡者一切皆轉。眾祐法輪聲三轉，諸天世間
<lb n="0503c17" ed="T"/>在法地者莫不遍聞，至<note n="0503031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">于＝於【明】</note><app n="0503031"><lem wit="【大】">于</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">於</rdg></app>第一四天王、忉
<lb n="0503c18" ed="T"/>利天、<note n="0503032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">焰＋（摩）【三】</note><note n="0503032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">焰＋（摩）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503032"><lem wit="【大】">焰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">焰摩</rdg></app>天、兜術天、不驕樂天、化應聲天，至諸
<lb n="0503c19" ed="T"/>梵界須臾遍聞。爾時，佛界三千日月萬二千
<lb n="0503c20" ed="T"/>天地皆大震動，是為佛眾祐，始於波羅<note n="0503033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00178;＝捺【元】，柰【明】</note><note n="0503033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00178;＝捺【元】，＝柰【明】</note><app n="0503033"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00178;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">捺</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">柰</rdg></app>以
<lb n="0503c21" ed="T"/>無上法輪轉未轉者，照無數度諸天人從是
<lb n="0503c22" ed="T"/>得道。</p><p id="pT02p0503c2203" place="inline">佛說是已，皆大歡喜。</p>
<lb n="0503c23" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><app type="＊" source="0503013"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>轉法輪經</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>